        Fixing cars and getting old ones to work again is something fantastic. You chose to become an auto mechanic
    *then
    roll 1d10
            if rollResult == 1{
            -> scenario3
            }
    -> chooseresidents
    
@electrician
    *say
        Running wire through a house and getting power to everything is phenomenal. You became a electrician
    *then
    roll 1d10
            if rollResult == 1{
            -> scenario3
            }
